info: This corpus is an automatically annotated version of data from the Parallel Bible Corpus (Mayer & Cysouw 2014) that has been reduced in scope for the purposes of crosslinguistic research. Metadata from the original PBC file is included in this dict for reference, as well as the license information and the automatic POS annotations. The first three characters of the filename corresponds to the ISO 639-3 code for the respective language. The `tagged` key in this dict contains a list of lists, with the first item in each sublist being the verse number (following PBC convention) and the second being a list of tuples in [word, POS] format where `unk` represents unknown tags.
license: This data is shared under a CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license, and can be used solely for research purposes. The data is a selection of non-contiguous verses from a translation for the purpose of crosslinguistic research. Copyright of selected verses of each translation is retained by the original copyright holders.

# vernacular_title: Slovenski Jubilejni prevod Nove zaveze
# english_title: Slovenian Jubilee Version of the New Testament

# copyright_long: Slovenian Jubilee Version of the New Testament
This translation was prepared under the auspices of United Bible Societies. It was first published by the Archdiocese of Ljubljana in 1985 and then, with corrections and revisions, in 1990 by United Bible Societies. It served as a basis of the Slovenian Standard Version of the Bible, which was published in 1996. This text is now used in the Slovenian Gideons' editions of the New Testament. Verses in square brackets […] are taken from the footnotes. For more information, please contact the Bible Society of Slovenia at www.svetopismo.si.
Slovenski Jubilejni prevod Nove zaveze Prevod je nastal na pobudo Združenih svetopisemskih družb. Prvič je izšel v Ljubljani leta 1985, popravljena in revidirana izdaja pa leta 1990. Služil je kot izhodišče za Slovenski standardni prevod, ki je izšel leta 1996. Besedilo je zdaj na voljo v gideonski izdaji slovenske Nove zaveze. Vrstice v oglatih oklepajih […] so prevzete iz opomb. Več informacij dobite na Svetopisemski družbi Slovenije, www.svetopismo.si.
